    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch Ch\\u7859?ng c\\'f3 c\\'e1i n\\'e0o b\\u7921?c m\\'ecnh h\\u417?n l\\'e0 khi xem phim c\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7913?a ng\\u7891?i c\\'f9ng h\\'e0ng gh\\u7871?ch\\u7859?ng bi\\u7871?t g\\'ec m\\'e0 c\\u7913? tinh t\\u432?\\u7899?ng thuy\\u7871?t minh cho b\\u7891? ra v\\u7867? c\\'e1i g\\'ec c\\u361?ng bi\\u7871?t,\\u273?i\\u7873?u g\\'ec c\\u361?ng hay. C\\'e1i th\\u7857?ng, d\\'f9 d\\u7889?t \\u273?\\u7863?c th\\'ec n\\'f3 c\\u361?ng ph\\u7843?i bi\\u7871?t I r\\u7855?c v\\u7899?i I ranl\\'e0 hai n\\u432?\\u7899?c kh\\'e1c nhau ch\\u7913?. Nh\\u432?ng c\\'e1i t\\u7897?i to nh\\u7845?t c\\u7911?a n\\'f3 l\\'e0 v\\u7915?a n\\'f3 v\\u7915?a v\\u259?ng n\\u432?\\u7899?c b\\u7885?t tung t\\'f3e nh\\u432? h\\'e0ng khuy\\u7871?n m\\'e3i cu\\u7889?i n\\u259?m. R\\u417?i c\\u7843? v\\'e0o g\\'f3i b\\u7855?p rangb\\u417? m\\'e0 hai \\u273?\\u7913?a c\\u7913? t\\'ec t\\'ec \\u273?\\'e1nh ch\\'e9n.- K\\u7879? hai \\u273?\\u7913?a \\u7903? b\\u7849?n \\u7845?y \\u273?i m\\'e0y. \\u258?n b\\u7855?p rang n\\'e0y. D\\u361?ng gi\\u417? ngang tay\\u273?\\u432?a m\\'ecnh b\\u7883?ch b\\u7855?p rang m\\u7899?i toanh. M\\'ecnh c\\u432?\\u7901?i nh\\u259?n nh\\u7903? c\\u7843?m \\u417?nn\\'f3, tuy c\\u361?ng c\\'f3 nh\\u432?ng Linh \\u273?\\'e3 \\u259?n ch\\u7859?ng c\\'f2n m\\u7897?t h\\u7841?t. Th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng c\\u7913? c\\u432?\\u7901?i kh\\'fac kh\\'edch m\\'e0 m\\'ecnh ch\\u7859?ng hi\\u7875?u l\\'fd do g\\'ec m\\'e0 n\\'f3 t\\u7921? s\\u432?\\u7899?\\u1080?\\u608? \\u273?\\u7871?n ph\\'e1t r\\u7891? nh\\u432? th\\u7871?.- \\u7914?, \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 khi y\\'eau nhau \\u273?\\u7871?n con ch\\u7845?y \\'e0 qu\\'ean n\\u432?\\u7899?c b\\u7885?t c\\u361?ng chia \\u273?\\u7873?u. M\\'ecnh kh\\u7869? n\\'f3i.-C\\u7843? l\\u361? \\u273?ang xem m\\u7897?t b\\u7897? phim kh\\'e1 l\\'e0 c\\'f3 t\\'ednh nh\\'e2n v\\u259?n, C\\'f4ng ch\\'faa h\\'f4n th\\u7907?s\\u259?n nh\\u432?ng cu\\u7889?i c\\'f9ng l\\u7841?i c\\u432?\\u7899?i ho\\'e0ng t\\u7917? l\\'e0m l\\u361? con g\\'e1i c\\u432?\\u7901?i h\\'f4 h\\u7889? v\\'ec phim\\u273?\\u7871?n \\u273?o\\u7841?n cu\\u7889?i, s\\u7855?p c\\'f3 k\\u7871?t h\\u7853?u \\u273?\\'fang nh\\u432? trong phim. Linh th\\'ec quay sang b\\u297?um\\'f4i ph\\'e1n.- Nh\\'e2n v\\u7853?t ch\\'ednh gi\\u7843? d\\u7889?i b\\u7887? x\\u7915?! n\\u7871?u \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 con g\\'e1i th\\'ec c\\u432?\\u7901?i ho\\'e0ngt\\u7917? nh\\u432?ng v\\u7851?n l\\'e9ng ph\\'e9ng v\\u7899?i th\\u7907? s\\u259?n ch\\u7913?. T\\'f4i l\\'e0 nh\\u432? th\\u7871? \\u273?\\u7845?y,ch\\u7859?ng t\\u7915? b\\u7887? ai c\\u7843? \\u273?\\'e2uH\\'f2a nghe xong t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\u7913? gi\\u7853?t l\\'ean gi\\u7853?t xu\\u7889?ng m\\u7845?y c\\'e1i, c\\'f3 l\\u7869? do c\\u7843? LyLy t\\u7921? nhi\\'ean l\\u7841?i khen n\\'f3 bi\\u7871?t ch\\u7885?n phim m\\'e0 xem l\\u7841?i c\\'f2n h\\'e0o ph\\'f3ng khao c\\u7843? b\\u7885?n. Th\\u7857?ng n\\'e0y u\\u7889?ng n\\u432?\\u7899?c \\u273?\\u7847?u tr\\u432?\\u7901?ng c\\'f2n t\\'ednh to\\'e1n so k\\'e8 t\\u7915?ng \\u273?\\u7891?ng, nh\\u432?ng v\\'ec s\\u297? g\\'e1i n\\'ean khi n\\'e0o v\\u7873? m\\u7899?i l\\u7897? ra b\\u7843?n ch\\u7845?t th\\'f4i. M\\'ecnh c\\u432?\\u7901?i th\\'eam t\\'ed kh\\'f3i l\\u7917?a v\\'e0o cho n\\'f3 s\\u432?\\u7899?\\u1080?\\u608? m\\u7897?t phen lu\\'f4n- \\u7914?, m\\u7897?t n\\u259?m c\\'f3 \\u273?\\'f4i ba l\\u7847?n g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7845?y H\\'f2a m\\u7899?i xu\\u7845?t th\\u7847?n nh\\u432? n\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7845?y nh\\u7881?. T\\'ed n\\u7919?a ra \\u273?\\u7915?ng c\\'f3 m\\'e0 \\u273?\\'f2i ti\\u7873?n \\u273?\\u7845?y nh\\'e9. Anh l\\'e0 anh ph\\u7843?i c\\u7843?m\\u417?n Ly Ly r\\u7891?i.Th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a ch\\u7881? bi\\u7871?t g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u khi Ly Ly \\u273?\\'f2i n\\'f3 x\\'e1c nh\\u7853?n l\\u7901?i n\\'f3i c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh,nh\\u432?ng b\\'e0n tay l\\u7841?i gi\\u417? n\\u7855?m \\u273?\\u7845?m ra c\\u7843?nh b\\'e1o m\\'ecnh. H\\u7871?t h\\u7885?c th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a th\\'ec m\\'ecnh quay s\\'e1ng tr\\'eau t\\u7913?c Linh lu\\'f4n.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - Em \\u7845?y \\'e0, c\\'f3 chi\\u7873?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c em th\\'ec ph\\u7843?i th\\'eam cha c\\u7911?a ho\\'e0ng t\\u7917? l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7841?igia gi\\'e0u x\\u7909? th\\'ec m\\u7899?i chi\\u7873?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c em.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Linh ch\\u7859?ng n\\'f3i ch\\u7859?ng r\\u7857?ng nh\\u432?ng l\\u7841?i nh\\u7855?m b\\'e0n ch\\'e2n m\\'ecnh m\\'e0 d\\u7851?m m\\u7841?nh b\\u7857?ng \\u273?\\'f4i b\\u7889?t \\u273?\\u7871? d\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7871?n 3 ph\\'e2n. Th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a k\\'eau to\\'e1n l\\'ean m\\u7897?t ti\\u7871?ng r\\'f5 to,l\\u7845?n \\'e1t c\\u7843? ti\\u7871?ng th\\'e9t trong phim l\\'e0m c\\u7843? ph\\'f2ng l\\u7841?i t\\u432?\\u7903?ng xem 2D \\'e2m thanh ch\\'e2n th\\u7921?c h\\u417?n c\\u7913? nh\\u432? l\\'e0 3D. Linh r\\u7889?i r\\'edt xin l\\u7895?i r\\u7891?i ng\\u7891?i xem ti\\u7871?p v\\u7899?i t\\u432? th\\u7871? ngoan ngo\\'e3n nh\\u432? con m\\'e8o con l\\'e0m \\u273?\\u7893? v\\u7905? ch\\u7853?u hoa nh\\u432?ng v\\'f4 t\\'ecnh ch\\u7913? kh\\'f4ngc\\u7889? \\'fd. H\\'f2a c\\'f3 ch\\'fat an \\u7911?i l\\'e0 Ly Ly c\\u7913? li\\'ean t\\u7909?c h\\u7887?i n\\'f3 c\\'f3 l\\'e0m sao kh\\'f4ng, c\\'f3 \\u273?au l\\u7855?m kh\\'f4ng.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch \\u272?\\u7871?n \\u273?o\\u7841?n cu\\u7889?i phim, ph\\'f2ng chi\\u7871?u t\\u7855?t \\u273?\\'e8n \\u273?\\u7875? th\\'eam ph\\u7847?n k\\u7883?ch t\\'ednh. M\\'ecnh gi\\u417?tay kho\\'e1c vai H\\'f2a th\\'e2n thi\\u7871?t ch\\u7859?ng k\\'e9m g\\'ec anh em s\\'e1t s\\u432?\\u7901?n an \\u7911?i n\\'f3 v\\u7873? c\\'e1i\\u273?\\u7841?p c\\u7911?a Linh. N\\'f3 v\\'e9o tay m\\'ecnh r\\'f5 \\u273?au, l\\u7849?m b\\u7849?m n\\'f3i g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3, c\\'f3 l\\u7869? l\\'e0 ch\\u7917?i m\\'ecnh nh\\u432?ng l\\'fac \\u273?\\'f3 \\'e2m thanh l\\u7899?n qu\\'e1 ch\\u7859?ng nghe th\\u7845?y g\\'ec c\\u7843?. T\\u7921? nhi\\'ean m\\'e0n h\\'ecnh t\\u7889?i om l\\u7841?i r\\u7891?i u\\u7923?nh m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i t\\u7841?o c\\u7843?m gi\\'e1c m\\u7841?nh cho ng\\u432?\\u7901?i xem. C\\u7913? nh\\u432? \\'f4ng tr\\u7901?iv\\u7915?a \\u273?\\'e1nh r\\u7855?m ra s\\u7845?m s\\'e9t m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i.Th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a \\'f4m m\\'ecnh! Tr\\u7901?i \\u417?i th\\u7857?ng bi\\u7871?\\u1080? \\u359?\\u614?\\'e1i! Hay l\\'e0 do ng\\u7891?i c\\u7841?nh m\\u7897?t ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\u7865?p trai nh\\u432? m\\'ecnh n\\'ean n\\'f3 ch\\u7907?t nh\\u7853?n ra th\\u7853?t con ng\\u432?\\u7901?i c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh? M\\u7897?t ti\\u7871?ng to \\u273?\\'f9ng n\\u7919?a l\\'e0m rung chuy\\u7875?n c\\'e0 ph\\'f2ng chi\\u7871?u. Th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a nh\\'e0o kh\\u7887?i gh\\u7871?, \\'f4m ch\\u7863?t l\\u7845?y m\\'ecnh.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh h\\u7871?t h\\u7891?n h\\'e9t l\\u7873?n \" M\\'e0y l\\'e0m g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7845?y, m\\'e0y l\\'e0m g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7845?y, bu\\'f4ng tao ra\"nh\\u432?ng H\\'f2a c\\'e0ng \\'f4m ch\\u7863?t h\\u417?n. Th\\'f4i xong m\\'ecnh r\\u7891?i. Qua \\u273?o\\u7841?n gay c\\u7845?n \\u273?\\'f3 th\\'ecc\\u361?ng l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7871?n k\\u7871?t phim, \\u273?\\'e8n m\\u7903? tr\\u7903? l\\u7841?i v\\'e0 th\\u7845?y Linh ch\\u7913? kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i l\\'e0 H\\'f2a.Th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a chuy\\u7875?n sang ng\\u7891?i c\\u7841?nh Ly Ly l\\'fac n\\'e0o m\\'e0 m\\'ecnh ch\\u7859?ng bi\\u7871?t th\\u7871?n\\'e0y. Linh nh\\'ecn m\\'ecnh m\\u7871?u m\\'e1o n\\'f3i.- Ra ngo\\'e0i \\u273?i... ra ngo\\'e0i \\u273?i m\\'e0. T\\'f4i s\\u7907? ti\\u7871?ng s\\u7845?m l\\u7855?m.- Nh\\u432?ng \\u273?\\'f3 c\\'f3 ph\\u7843?i l\\'e0 ti\\u7871?ng s\\u7845?m \\u273?\\'e2u, gi\\'e1 ti\\u7871?ng s\\u7845?m th\\'f4i m\\'e0.- T\\'f4i kh\\'f4ng ph\\'e2n bi\\u7879?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c. T\\'f4i s\\u7907? ti\\u7871?ng s\\u7845?m nh\\u7845?t \\u273?\\u7845?yLinh n\\'f3i v\\u7899?igi\\u7885?ng van n\\'e0i c\\u7913? nh\\u432? kh\\'f3c \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i.- \\u7914? th\\'ec ra.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh \\u273?\\u432?a Linh ra trong t\\'ecnh tr\\u7841?ng Linh ng\\u432?\\u7901?i m\\u7873?m nh\\u361?n nh\\u432? c\\u7885?ng b\\'fan, runr\\u7849?y v\\'ec s\\u7907? v\\'e0 v\\u7851?n \\'f4m ch\\u7863?t m\\'ecnh. \\u272?\\'f9a ch\\u7913? khi m\\'ecnh \\u273?i ngang qua Ly Ly, H\\'f2av\\'e0 D\\u361?ng th\\'ec ch\\u7859?ng \\u273?\\u7913?a n\\'e0o \\u273?\\u7875? \\'fd c\\u7843?, nh\\u7919?ng \\u273?\\u7913?a xem phim c\\u361?n v\\u7853?y. C\\u7843? l\\u361?\\u273?ang xem c\\u7843?nh cu\\u7889?i khi hai nh\\'e2n v\\u7853?t ch\\'ednh h\\'f4n nhau c\\u7913? nh\\u432? th\\u7875? ch\\'ednh b\\u7885?nn\\'f3 \\u273?ang h\\'f4n nhau. Duy ch\\u7881? c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t con b\\'e9, c\\'f3 l\\u7869? b\\u7857?ng tu\\u7893?i v\\u7899?i Linh c\\u7913? nh\\'edum\\'e0y nh\\'ecn c\\u259?m gi\\u7853?n gi\\u7889?ng nh\\u432? v\\u7915?a c\\u432?\\u7899?p m\\u7845?t b\\u7883?ch b\\u7855?p rang b\\u417? v\\u7853?y.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh d\\'ecu Linh ra sofa \\u7903? ngo\\'e0i ng\\u7891?i m\\u7897?t l\\'e1t th\\'ec em d\\u7847?n t\\u7881?nh l\\u7841?i. Trong l\\'fac \\u7845?yth\\'ec Linh v\\u7851?n \\'f4m ch\\u7863?t l\\u7845?y m\\'ecnh. L\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y m\\'ecnh c\\u361?ng cho\\'e1ng v\\'e1n kh\\'f4ng k\\'e9m. Ai \\u273?i qua c\\u7913? t\\u432?\\u7903?ng hai \\u273?\\u7913?a l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t \\u273?\\'f4i \\u273?ang y\\'eau \\u273?ang ng\\u7891?i t\\'e2m s\\u7921? t\\'ecnh c\\u7843?m r\\u7845?t l\\'e0 m\\u361?i m\\u7851?n. M\\'ecnh l\\u7847?n n\\'e0y c\\'f3 hai c\\'e1i may kh\\'f4ng th\\u7875? t\\u7843? h\\u7871?t n\\u7895?i sung s\\u432?\\u7899?\\u1080?\\u608?. Th\\u7913? nh\\u7845?t l\\'e0 Linh \\'f4m m\\'ecnh ch\\u7913? kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a, th\\u7913? hail\\'e0 l\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i em c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t k\\u7881? ni\\u7879?m chung th\\'e2n m\\u7853?t v\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7865?p nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y.Linh tr\\'f4ng kh\\'f4ng kh\\u7887?e ch\\'fat n\\'e0o,nh\\u432?ng m\\'ecnh c\\u361?ng \\u273?ang say n\\u7855?ng m\\u7845?t r\\u7891?i.Hai \\u273?\\u7913?a c\\u7913? nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y cho \\u273?\\u7871?n khi n\\'e0o Linh tr\\u7903? l\\u7841?i b\\'ecnh th\\u432?\\u7901?ng th\\'ec th\\'f4i.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Em d\\u7847?n d\\u7847?n bu\\'f4ng m\\'ecnh ra, t\\u7915?ng ch\\'fat m\\u7897?t d\\u7883?ch ra m\\u7897?t kho\\u7843?ng c\\'e1ch v\\u7899?im\\'ecnh v\\'e0 sau \\u273?\\'f3 th\\'ec \\u273?\\u7887? m\\u7863?t gi\\u7843?i th\\'edch.- T\\'f4i s\\u7907? ti\\u7871?ng s\\u7845?m t\\u7915? nh\\u7887?. L\\'fac \\u273?\\'f3... L\\'fac \\u273?\\'f3 t\\'f4i c\\u7913? t\\u432?\\u7903?ng l\\'e0 Ly Ly n\\'ean anh \\u273?\\u7915?ng t\\u432?\\u7903?ng b\\u7903? \\u273?\\'e2y nh\\'e9. Nh\\u432? th\\u7871? n\\'e0y th\\'ec thi\\u7879?t cho t\\'f4i qu\\'e1- \\'d4m anh ch\\u7853?t c\\u7913?ng nh\\u432? g\\u7889?i \\'f4m th\\'edch th\\'e9 l\\u7841?i c\\'f2n gi\\u7843? v\\u7901?. M\\'ecnh gi\\u7843? v\\u7901? l\\u7849?m b\\u7849?m \\u273?\\u7875? Linh nghe th\\u7845?y.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Linh quay m\\u7863?t ra ch\\u7895? kh\\'e1c t\\u7887? ra kh\\'f4ng quan t\\'e2m nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec m\\'ecnh n\\'f3i. Nh\\u432?n gem \\u273?ang x\\u7845?u h\\u7893? v\\'e0 ng\\u7841?i ng\\'f9ng khi nh\\u7899? l\\u7841?i l\\u7855?m \\u273?\\'e2y}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\u7845?y ph\\'fat sau phim h\\u7871?t th\\'ec c\\u7843? ph\\'f2ng chen nhau \\u273?i ra. Con b\\'e9 kia th\\u7845?y m\\'ecnh th\\'ec l\\u7841?i cau c\\'f3 l\\u432?\\u7901?m m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i r\\'f5 d\\'e0i, \\u273?\\'e3 v\\u7853?y n\\'f3 c\\'f2n ch\\u7881? tr\\u7887? cho \\u273?\\'e1m b\\u7841?n v\\'e0 c\\u7843? b\\u7885?n h\\'f9a v\\u7899?i nhau n\\'f3i g\\'ec \\u273?\\u7845?y kh\\'f4ng r\\'f5 n\\u7919?a. M\\'ecnh xin th\\u7873? l\\'e0 n\\u7871?u nh\\u432? b\\'e2y gi\\u7901? h\\u7855?t h\\u417?i v\\'ec c\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7913?a n\\'e0o n\\'f3i x\\u7845?u th\\'ec c\\u361?ng ch\\u7859?ng ng\\u7841?c nhi\\'ean l\\u7855?m. Th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng,H\\'f2a v\\u7899?i Ly Ly c\\u361?ng \\u273?i ra ngay sau \\u273?\\u7845?y. V\\u7915?a g\\u7863?p th\\'ec tr\\u432?\\u7899?c khi h\\u7887?i nguy\\'eannh\\'e2n t\\u7841?i sao m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i Linh ra tr\\u432?\\u7899?c th\\'ec th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng c\\u7913? \\'f4m b\\u7909?ng c\\u432?\\u7901?i ng\\u7863?t ng\\u7869?o.- M\\'e0y b\\u7883? th\\u7871? l\\'e2u ch\\u432?a? C\\u432?\\u7901?i g\\'ec m\\'e0 s\\u7855?p s\\'e1i quai h\\'e0m \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i r\\u7891?i \\u273?\\u7845?y?M\\'ecnh h\\u7887?i.- Th\\u7871? l\\'fac n\\'e3y c\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7913?a n\\'e0o nh\\'ecn m\\'e0y v\\u7899?i \\'e1nh m\\u7855?t vi\\'ean \\u273?\\u7841?n kh\\'f4ng h\\u7843? H\\u432?ng. Th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng v\\u7851?n c\\u432?\\u7901?i.- Sao m\\'e0y bi\\u7871?t, c\\'f2n tao th\\'ec ch\\u7859?ng hi\\u7875?u g\\'ec c\\u7843?.- N\\'f3 l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7913?a ng\\u7891?i c\\'f9ng h\\'e0ng v\\u7899?i m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\u7845?y, m\\'e0y c\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7875? \\'fd kh\\'f4ng?- \\u272?i qua tao c\\u361?ng th\\u7845?y th\\u7871?, nh\\u432?ng c\\'f3 li\\'ean quan g\\'ec v\\u7899?i vi\\u7879?c m\\'e0y c\\u432?\\u7901?i nh\\u432? th\\u7857?ng \\u273?i\\'ean v\\u7853?y.- Th\\u7871? b\\u7855?p rang b\\u417? tao \\u273?\\u432?a m\\'e0y ch\\'e9n h\\u7871?t r\\u7891?i \\'e0. N\\'f3i th\\u7853?t v\\u7899?i m\\'e0y l\\'e0kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i c\\u7911?a tao \\u273?\\'e2u, con b\\'e9 \\u273?\\'f3 \\u273?i toa-let th\\'ec ph\\u7843?i, n\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7875? \\u7903? b\\'ean c\\u7841?nh n\\'ean ti\\u7879?n tay tao l\\u7845?y \\u273?\\u432?a m\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7845?y. Khi b\\u7883?ch b\\u7855?p rang v\\u7915?a \\u273?\\u7871?ntay m\\'e0y th\\'ec c\\u361?ng l\\'e0 l\\'fac n\\'f3 quay l\\u7841?i gh\\u7871? ng\\u7891?i \\u273?\\u7845?y. Gi\\u7901? th\\'ec m\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e3 bi\\u7871?t t\\u7841?i sao n\\'f3 nh\\'ecn \\u273?\\u7875?u m\\'e0y ch\\u432?a?}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh ng\\u7899? ra khi th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng n\\'f3i th\\u7871?. Th\\u7871? l\\'e0 ng\\'e0y h\\'f4m nay m\\u7897?t n\\u7917?a H\\'e0 N\\u7897?ibi\\u7871?t chuy\\u7879?n n\\'e0y r\\u7891?i. C\\'f3 l\\u7869? con b\\'e9 kia \\u273?ang c\\'f9ng v\\u7899?i c\\'e1c b\\u7841?n loan tin n\\'e0ykh\\u7855?p Vincom m\\u7845?t. Kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7841?y nhanh l\\'ean m\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7907?i \\u273?\\u7871?n l\\'fac c\\'f3 ai ch\\u7881? m\\u7863?t m\\'e0n\\'f3i th\\'ec h\\u7871?t \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng v\\u7873? qu\\'ea m\\u7865?. \\u272?\\'fang l\\'e0 tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng l\\'e1nh n\\u7841?n c\\'f2n g\\u7863?p tai n\\u7841?n!Ch\\u7881? t\\u7841?i m\\'ecnh k\\'e9m th\\'f4ng minh, ch\\u7885?n to\\'e0n \\u273?\\u7913?a b\\u7841?n t\\u7889?t th\\'f4i.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch L\\'fac n\\'e0y Linh c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\'e3 kh\\'f4ng c\\'f2n d\\u7845?u hi\\u7879?u g\\'ec gi\\u7889?ng nh\\u432? trong ph\\'f2ng chi\\u7871?un\\u7919?a. C\\u7843? b\\u7885?n k\\'e9o nhau \\u273?i \\u259?n pizza \\u7903? d\\u432?\\u7899?i t\\u7847?ng, r\\u7891?i c\\u7843? kem n\\u7919?a. Ti\\u7873?n th\\'ec c\\'f3 bao nhi\\'eau g\\'f3p b\\u7845?y nhi\\'eau, may m\\'e0 nh\\u7901? v\\'e0o s\\u7921? h\\'e0o ph\\'f3ng b\\u7845?t th\\u432?\\u7901?ng c\\u7911?a th\\u7857?ng H\\'f2a v\\'e0 v\\'ed ti\\u7873?n d\\'e0y nh\\u432? cu\\u7889?n s\\u7893? c\\u7911?a D\\u361?ng n\\'ean c\\u7843? bu\\u7893?i n\\u259?m \\u273?\\u432?a \\u259?n ch\\u417?i h\\u7871?t c\\u7905?. Khi ng\\u7891?i th\\'ec nhi\\u7873?u chuy\\u7879?n ng\\'e0y x\\u432?a l\\'f4i ra n\\'f3i l\\u7855?m. H\\u7885?c h\\'e0nh th\\'ec b\\'e2ygi\\u7901? \\u273?\\u7889? \\u273?\\u7913?a n\\'e0o gi\\u7843?i \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c b\\'e0i to\\'e1n n\\'e2ng cao c\\u7845?p 1, nh\\u432?ng tr\\'f2 ngh\\u7883?ch ng\\u7907?mh\\u7871?t c\\u7905? ng\\'e0y tr\\u432?\\u7899?c th\\'ec c\\u7913? nh\\u432? v\\u7915?a \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c ch\\u417?i h\\'f4m qua. N\\'e0o l\\'e0 n\\'e9m qu\\u7843? th\\u7889? isang l\\u7899?p b\\'ean c\\u7841?nh, \\u273?\\u7849?y th\\u7857?ng n\\'e0o nh\\'e1t g\\'e1i v\\'e0o ph\\'f2ng v\\u7879? sinh n\\u7919? trong gi\\u7901? ra ch\\u417?i, r\\u7891?i thay phi\\'ean n\\'e9m phao cho nhau khi thi cu\\u7889?i n\\u259?m. Nh\\u7899? l\\u7841?i \\u273?\\u7875? k\\u7875? th\\'ecc\\'f3 m\\'e0 h\\u7871?t ng\\'e0y.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng chuy\\u7875?n \\u273?\\u7873? t\\'e0i r\\u7891?i n\\u7893? ph\\'e1t s\\'fang \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean lu\\'f4n- Th\\u7871? k\\u7871? ho\\u7841?ch ti\\u7871?p theo l\\'e0 g\\'ec h\\u7843? m\\u7845?y v\\u7907? ch\\u7891?ng?}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh nh\\'ecn Linh, H\\'f2a nh\\'ecn Ly Ly r\\u7891?i c\\u7843? b\\u7889?n \\u273?\\u7913?a \\u273?\\u7873?u \\u273?\\u7891?ng thanh \\u273?\\'e1p- V\\u7907? ch\\u7891?ng n\\'e0o c\\u417??- V\\u7869? chuy\\u7879?n! T\\'f4i bi\\u7871?t t\\u7887?ng r\\u7891?i, \\u273?\\u7883?nh gi\\u7845?u ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\'e3 y\\'eau v\\'e0 \\u273?\\'e3 c\\'f3 v\\u7907?ch\\u7855?c. D\\u361?ng b\\u297?u m\\'f4i.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Ly Ly v\\u7899?i Linh th\\'ec ch\\u7881? c\\u432?\\u7901?i tr\\u7917?, lu\\'f4n mi\\u7879?ng n\\'f3i \" Kh\\'f4ng \\u7841? v\\u7899?i \\u273?\\'e2u \\u7841?\". C\\'f2nm\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i H\\'f2a th\\'ec vung n\\u7855?m \\u273?\\u7845?m l\\'ean b\\u7843?o th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng chuy\\u7875?n ch\\u7911? \\u273?\\u7873?.- Ng\\u7841?i c\\'e1i qu\\'e1i g\\'ec, to\\'e0n thanh ni\\'ean v\\u7899?i nhau m\\'e0 c\\u7913? gi\\u7843? v\\u7901? th\\u7871?. Th\\'edch th\\'ec n\\'f3i l\\'e0 th\\'edch. Y\\'eau th\\'ec n\\'f3i l\\'e0 y\\'eau l\\'e0 xong xu\\'f4i h\\u7871?t. N\\u7871?u b\\u7883? t\\u7915? ch\\u7889?ith\\'ec y\\'eau l\\u7841?i t\\u7915? \\u273?\\u7847?u. C\\u7913? nh\\u432? tao \\u273?\\'e2y n\\'e0y, ch\\u7881? n\\'f3i v\\'e0i c\\'e2u l\\'e0 v\\u7907? tao \\u273?\\u7893? nh\\u432? ng\\u7843? r\\u7841?.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch \\u272?\\'fang l\\'fac n\\'e0y th\\'ec chu\\'f4ng \\u273?i\\u7879?n tho\\u7841?i trong qu\\u7847?n D\\u361?ng reo l\\'ean. N\\'f3 m\\u7903? m\\'e0y th\\'ec \\u273?\\u7893?i gi\\u7885?ng ngay. H\\'ecnh nh\\u432? b\\u7841?n g\\'e1i g\\u7885?i \\u273?i\\u7879?n ki\\u7875?m tra v\\'e0 n\\'f3 \\u273?ang c\\u7889? t\\u7887? ra r\\u7845?t t\\u7921? k\\u7881? khi hai \\u273?\\u7913?a c\\'e3i nhau.- A l\\'f4 v\\u7907? \\'e0, anh \\u273?ang chong \\u273?\\'e8n khi tr\\u7901?i s\\'e1ng, d\\u7885?n m\\'e1ng l\\u7907?n v\\'e0obu\\u7893?i tr\\u432?a v\\'e0 ng\\u7855?m m\\u432?a \\u273?\\u7871?n chi\\u7873?u t\\u7889?i khi kh\\'f4ng c\\u7899? v\\u7907? \\u273?\\'e2y n\\'e0y...\\u272?\\'e2u, anh c\\'f3 \\u273?i \\u273?\\'e2u \\u273?\\'e2u, \\u273?\\u7853?p v\\'e0o m\\u7863?t \\u273?\\u7913?a n\\'e0o n\\'f3i v\\u7907? th\\u7871? \\u273?\\u7845?y. Th\\u7871? h\\'f4m nay v\\u7907? ngh\\u297? l\\'e0m \\'e0, v\\u7853?y anh v\\u7873? \\u273?\\'f3n \\u273?i ch\\u417?i nh\\'e9.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Xoen xo\\'e9t c\\'e1i m\\u7891?m xong l\\'e0 D\\u361?ng xin ki\\u7871?u v\\u7873? s\\u7899?m v\\'e0 h\\u7865?n g\\u7863?p l\\u7841?i v\\'e0o m\\u7897?tng\\'e0y \\u273?\\u7865?p tr\\u7901?i n\\'e0o \\u273?\\u7845?y. Tr\\u432?\\u7899?c khi v\\u7873? n\\'f3 \\u273?\\u432?a m\\u7855?t nh\\'ecn c\\u7863?p gi\\'f2 c\\u7911?a Linh l\\u7847?n cu\\u7889?i l\\'e0m m\\'ecnh b\\u7921?c qu\\'e1 ch\\u7859?ng bi\\u7871?t l\\'e0m th\\u7871? n\\'e0o. M\\'ecnh hi\\u7875?u ch\\u7881? l\\'e0 b\\'ecnh th\\u432?\\u7901?ngv\\'ec n\\u7871?u m\\'ecnh l\\'e0 n\\'f3 th\\'ec m\\'ecnh c\\u361?ng nh\\'ecn Linh nh\\u432? th\\u7871?, nh\\u432?ng m\\'e0 v\\u7851?n th\\u7845?y kh\\'f3ch\\u7883?u qu\\'e1. M\\'e0 n\\'f3 v\\u7873? c\\u361?ng \\u273?\\'fang l\\'fac th\\u7853?t, m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i H\\'f2a \\u273?\\u7873?u c\\u7847?n c\\'f3 kh\\'f4ng gian ri\\'eang danh cho hai c\\'f4 g\\'e1i m\\'e0 ch\\u432?a bi\\u7871?t \\u273?u\\u7893?i kh\\'e9o th\\u7857?ng D\\u361?ng \\u273?i \\u273?\\'e2u \\u273?\\'e2y.Ngay sau \\u273?\\'f3 H\\'f2a v\\u7899?i Ly Ly li\\u7873?n ch\\'e0o m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\u7875? t\\'e1ch ra t\\'ecm kh\\'f4ng kh\\'ed ri\\'eang.Tr\\'f4ng H\\'f2a b\\u7899?t nh\\'e1t gan h\\u417?n v\\'e0 t\\u7887? ra \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 m\\u7897?t ng\\u432?\\u7901?i \\u273?\\'e0n \\'f4ng th\\u7853?t th\\u7909?r\\u7891?i, d\\'f9 cho n\\'f3 ch\\u7859?ng c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t ch\\'fat c\\u417? b\\u7855?p n\\'e0o v\\'e0 b\\u7909?ng ch\\u7881? c\\'f3 m\\u7897?t m\\'fai \\u273?angtr\\u432?\\u417?ng ph\\'ecnh l\\'ean v\\'ec pizza v\\'e0 kem.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch L\\'fac n\\'e0y ch\\u7881? c\\'f2n m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i Linh c\\'f2n ng\\u7891?i l\\u7841?i. Linh quay sang h\\u7887?i m\\'ecnh kinhph\\'ed c\\'f2n bao nhi\\'eau \\u273?\\u7875? c\\'f2n bi\\u7879?t li\\u7879?u ch\\u7885?n ch\\u7895? m\\'e0 ch\\u417?i.- C\\'f2n \\u273?\\u7911? \\u273?\\u7875? c\\'f3 th\\u7875? l\\'ean ph\\u7889? l\\u432?\\u7907?n l\\u7901? r\\u7891?i mua c\\'e1i g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3 \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c kh\\'f4ng?- V\\u7851?n c\\'f2n 50 ngh\\'ecn, n\\u7871?u nh\\u432? \\u259?n ch\\u417?i m\\'e0 thi\\u7871?u th\\'ec anh s\\u7869? b\\u7855?t em\\u273?\\u7913?ng m\\'faa \\u273?\\u7875? thu ti\\u7873?n \\u273?\\'e2y. \\'c0, hay l\\'e0 m\\'ecnh l\\'e0m th\\u7871? \\u273?i. \\'dd ki\\u7871?n hay ph\\u7843?i kh\\'f4ng- Hay c\\'e1i \\u273?\\u7847?u anh \\u7845?y. Anh n\\'f3i th\\'ec c\\u7903?i tr\\u7847?n khoe 36 c\\'e1i x\\u432?\\u417?ng s\\u432?\\u7901?nr\\u7891?i ngo\\'e1y m\\'f4ng tr\\u432?\\u7899?c m\\u7863?t thi\\'ean h\\u7841? \\u273?i. Th\\'f4i, m\\'ecnh \\u273?i l\\'e0m m\\u7897?t v\\'f2ng,t\\'ecm ch\\u7895? n\\'e0o ng\\u7891?i l\\'e2u l\\'e2u r\\u7891?i t\\u7889?i v\\u7873? \\u259?n n\\u7889?t c\\u7895? th\\u7915?a \\u273?i.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch M\\'ecnh g\\u7853?t \\u273?\\u7847?u d\\'f9 cho c\\'e1i vi\\u7877?n c\\u7843?nh ph\\'eda tr\\u432?\\u7899?c kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i ho\\'e0n h\\u7843?o l\\u7855?m,nh\\u432?ng Linh ch\\u7845?p nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'ec m\\'ecnh c\\u361?ng ch\\u7845?p nh\\u7853?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c. Linh mu\\u7889?n g\\'ec th\\'ec m\\'ecnh s\\u7869? l\\'e0m nh\\u432? v\\u7853?y d\\'f9 bi\\u7871?t r\\u7857?ng Linh thi\\u7879?t th\\'f2i khi \\u273?i v\\u7899?i m\\'ecnh. Linhc\\'f3 l\\u7869? l\\'fac n\\'e0y \\u273?ang ng\\u7891?i \\u7903? \\u273?\\'e2u \\u273?\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7865?p v\\'e0 th\\'fa v\\u7883? h\\u417?n nhi\\u7873?u l\\u7847?n khi \\u273?i v\\u7899?i m\\'ecnh n\\u7871?u nh\\u432? th\\u7857?ng \\u273?\\'f3 kh\\'f4ng ph\\u7843?i l\\'e0 m\\'ecnh. Khi m\\'ecnh \\'fd th\\u7913?c \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c \\u273?i\\u7873?u n\\'e0y th\\'ec m\\'ecnh c\\'e0ng tr\\'e2n tr\\u7885?ng t\\'f9ng gi\\'e2y ph\\'fat n\\'e0y h\\u417?n n\\u7919?a. Tr\\'ean \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng, m\\'ecnh v\\u7915?angh\\u297? ra nh\\u7919?ng c\\'e2u chuy\\u7879?n th\\u7853?t vui \\u273?\\u7875? l\\u7847?n \\u273?\\u7847?u ti\\'ean \\u273?i ch\\u417?i chung c\\u7911?a hai \\u273?\\u7913?a th\\u7853?t l\\'e0 \\u273?\\u7865?p \\u273?\\u7869? v\\'e0 kh\\'f3 qu\\'ean. Nh\\u432?ng c\\u361?ng ch\\'ednh t\\u7915? l\\'fac n\\'e0y m\\'ecnh \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7855?t \\u273?\\u7847?u ngh\\u297? \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u7897?t c\\'f4ng vi\\u7879?c \\u273?\\u7875? gi\\'fap cho m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i Linh s\\u7869? c\\'f3 nhi\\u7873?u ng\\'e0y vui nh\\u432?th\\u7871? n\\'e0y trong th\\u7901?i gian t\\u7899?i.}\\line \\line \\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
