    "name": "Chưa Đặt Tên",
    "content": "{\\rtf1\\ansi\\ansicpg1252\\uc1\\htmautsp\\deff2{\\fonttbl{\\f0\\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\\f2\\fcharset0 Georgia;}{\\f3\\fcharset0 Noto Serif;}}{\\colortbl\\red0\\green0\\blue0;\\red255\\green255\\blue255;}\\loch\\hich\\dbch\\pard\\plain\\ltrpar\\itap0{\\lang1033\\fs30\\f3\\cf0 \\cf0\\qj{\\cf1 \\cf1\\ql{{\\ltrch - D\\u7853?y \\u273?i n\\'e0o, \\u273?ang c\\u7847?n m\\u7897?t thanh ni\\'ean kh\\u7887?e m\\u7841?nh, ch\\u259?m ch\\u7881?, kh\\'f4ng ng\\u7841?i d\\u7885?n d\\u7865?p v\\'e0 lau ch\\'f9i g\\u7845?p. Anh qua lu\\'f4n nh\\'e9.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Ch\\u432?a \\u273?\\u7871?n 7 gi\\u7901? s\\'e1ng Linh \\u273?\\'e3 nh\\'e1y m\\'e1y nheo nh\\'e9o g\\u7885?i m\\'ecnh v\\u7899?i gi\\u7885?ng \\u273?i\\u7879?u c\\u7913? nh\\u432? m\\'e1i nh\\'e0 s\\u7855?p s\\u7853?p \\u273?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i. N\\u7871?u l\\'e0 m\\'ecnh ng\\'e0y x\\u432?a thi k\\u7871?t c\\u7909?c c\\u7911?a cu\\u7897?c \\u273?i\\u7879?n tho\\u7841?i n\\'e0y s\\u7869? l\\'e0 \"t\\u7921? lo \\u273?i con \\u273?i\\'ean, k\\u7879? m\\u7865? m\\'e0y\". V\\u7853?y m\\'e0 b\\'e2y gi\\u7901? kh\\'f4ng hi\\u7875?u sao m\\'ecnh nhi\\u7877?m virut d\\u7841?i g\\'e1i \\u273?\\u7871?n kinh kh\\u7911?ng nh\\u432? th\\u7871?. Ti\\u7871?t th\\'e1ng 12 m\\'e0 ph\\u7843?i \\u273?\\u7841?p ch\\u259?n cho\\'e0ng d\\u7853?y trong t\\'ecnh tr\\u7841?ng l\\u7841?nh \\u273?\\u7871?n m\\u7913?c \\u7845?y c\\'f2n b\\u7883? sun th\\'ec ch\\u7859?ng kh\\'e1c g\\'ec \\u273?\\'e1nh \\u273?\\'f3. Nh\\u432?ng c\\u361?ng t\\u7841?i c\\'e1i mi\\u7879?ng h\\u7841?i c\\'e1i th\\'e2n h\\u7871?t c\\u7843?, ai b\\u7843?o m\\'ecnh toang to\\'e1c l\\'e0 l\\'fac n\\'e0o c\\u7847?n th\\'ec c\\u7913? g\\u7885?i n\\'ean m\\u7899?i th\\'e0nh ra th\\u7871? n\\'e0y \\u273?\\'e2y. \\'d4i \\u273?\\'fang l\\'e0 sung s\\u432?\\u7899?\\u1080?\\u608? c\\'e1i th\\'e2n n\\'e0y! C\\'f3 l\\u7869? nh\\u7919?ng g\\'ec Linh mu\\u7889?n m\\'ecnh l\\'e0m, mu\\u7889?n m\\'ecnh gi\\u7843?i quy\\u7871?t th\\'ec bao nhi\\'eau c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng \\u273?\\u7911? c\\u7843?.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Nh\\u259?n nh\\'f3 than v\\'e3n h\\u7891?i l\\'e2u th\\'ec cu\\u7889?i c\\'f9ng m\\'ecnh v\\u7851?n ph\\u7843?i nh\\u7887?m d\\u7853?y trong t\\'ecnh tr\\u7841?ng \\u273?\\u7847?u b\\'f9 r\\u259?ng b\\u7921?a. M\\u7845?t 10 ph\\'fat \\u273?\\u7875? l\\u7845?y l\\u7841?i phong \\u273?\\u7897?, l\\'f2 d\\'f2 d\\u7851?n xe ra th\\'ec \\u273?\\u7841?p ph\\u7843?i ch\\'e2n tr\\u7889?ng \\u273?au c\\'f2n h\\u417?n b\\u7883? ho\\u7841?n. T\\u7915? nh\\'e0 m\\'ecnh qua ch\\u7895? Linh ch\\u7881? m\\u7845?t 10 ph\\'fat nh\\u432?ng c\\'e1i l\\u7841?nh s\\'e1ng ra \\u273?\\'e3 \\u273?\\'e1nh b\\u7841?i c\\'e1i ki\\u7875?u m\\u7863?c th\\u7901?i trang h\\u417?n th\\u7901?i ti\\u7871?t c\\u7911?a m\\'ecnh. L\\'fac n\\'e0y m\\'ecn ch\\u7881? m\\u7863?c \\u273?\\u7897?c c\\'e1i \\'e1o ph\\'f4ng b\\'ean trong v\\'e0 \\'e1o kho\\'e1c ka-ki cao c\\u7893?, d\\u432?\\u7899?i ch\\'e2n th\\'ec x\\u7887? \\u273?\\'f4i t\\u7887? ong \\u273?i nh\\u7847?m t\\u7915? l\\'fac trong nh\\'e0 t\\u7855?m. \\u272?\\u7871?n n\\u417?i th\\'ec th\\u7845?y Linh co ro ng\\u7891?i x\\u7893?m \\u7903? g\\'f3c v\\u432?\\u7901?n b\\'ean ngo\\'e0i, con Bin th\\'ec tr\\'f4ng d\\u7877? th\\u432?\\u417?ng \\u273?\\u7871?n k\\'ec l\\u7841?. Ng\\u432?\\u7901?i v\\'e0 ch\\'f3 \\u273?\\u7875?u nh\\u7893?m d\\u7853?y khi m\\'ecnh b\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e0o, Linh li\\u7873?n ch\\u7881? con Bin m\\'e0 m\\'e1ch t\\u7897?i. C\\'f3 m\\'f9i g\\'ec \\u273?\\'f3 r\\u7845?t kh\\'f3 ch\\u7883?u.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - Anh v\\'e0o m\\'e0 xem, ch\\u7881? v\\'ec th\\u432?\\u417?ng n\\'f3 m\\'e0 t\\'f4i l\\u7841?i r\\u432?\\u7899?c h\\u7885?a v\\'e0o th\\'e2n. Kh\\u7893? th\\'e2n t\\'f4i, m\\u7897?t c\\'e1i ch\\'e2n th\\'ec b\\u7883? t\\u7853?t, c\\'e1i c\\'f2n l\\u7841?i th\\'ec d\\u7851?m ph\\u7843?i ph\\'e2n ch\\'f3. - Linh ch\\'eca c\\'e1i ch\\'e2n kh\\'f4ng b\\u7883? \\u273?au cho m\\'ecnh th\\u7845?y.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - B\\u7889?c m\\'f9i qu\\'e1! - M\\'ecnh b\\u7883?t m\\u361?i}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - \\u7914? th\\'ec sao! Anh th\\u7917? d\\u7851?m ph\\'e2n ch\\'f3 xem, d\\u7877? c\\'f2n kh\\'f3 ng\\u7917?i h\\u417?n c\\u7843? t\\'f4i v\\'ec anh b\\u7883? h\\'f4i ch\\'e2n s\\u7861?n m\\'e0.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - Anh kh\\'f4ng h\\'f4i ch\\'e2n, em th\\u7917? ng\\u7917?i \\u273?i!}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - \\u272?\\u7891? v\\'f4 duy\\'ean! \\u258?n n\\'f3i v\\u7899?i con g\\'e1i th\\u7871? \\'e0.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - Ai b\\u7843?o em l\\'e0 con g\\'e1i, em l\\'e0 Th\\'f4i Ch\\u7845?n Linh th\\'ec c\\'f3.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch - \\u7914? th\\'ec t\\'f4i l\\'e0 Linh th\\u7889?i ch\\'e2n \\u273?\\u7845?y, nh\\u432?ng c\\'f3 ch\\u7871?t t\\'f4i c\\u361?ng kh\\'f4ng d\\u7885?n b\\'e3i chi\\u7871?n tr\\u432?\\u7901?ng kia \\u273?\\'e2u.}\\line \\line {\\ltrch Con Bin ch\\u7881? bi\\u7871?t k\\'eau \\u432? \\u7917? r\\u7891?i ngeo ngu\\u7849?y \\u273?u\\'f4i l\\u7845?y l\\'f2ng, c\\'f2n m\\'ecnh th\\'ec c\\'f2n ch\\u7859?ng hi\\u7875?u t\\u7841?i sao Linh l\\u7841?i than v\\'e3n nh\\u432? th\\u7871?. Nh\\u432?ng khi m\\'ecnh b\\u432?\\u7899?c v\\'e0o nh\\'e0 th\\'ec \\'f4i th\\'f4i su\\'fdt n\\u7919?a th\\'ec n\\'f4n s\\u7841?ch \\'edt b\\u7885?t \\u273?\\'e1nh r\\u259?ng nu\\u7889?t ph\\u7843?i t\\u7915? h\\'f4m qua v\\'e0 l\\'fac s\\'e1ng. Con Bin \\u273?i b\\u7853?y ra kh\\u7855?p nh\\'e0, b\\'e3i to, b\\'e3i b\\'e9 thi nhau b\\u7889?c m\\'f9i kinh ho\\'e0ng c\\'f2n h\\u417?n c\\u7843? b\\'e3i tha ma hay c\\'e1i c\\u7889?ng ngo\\'e0i \\u273?\\u432?\\u7901?ng kia. Ngay \\u273?\\u7871?n con Bin c\\'f2n kh\\'f4ng ch\\u7883?u \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c th\\'ec th\\u7843?o n\\'e0o Linh d\\'f9 \\u273?au ch\\'e2n c\\u361?ng c\\u7889? l\\u7871? l\\u7871?t ra kh\\u7887?i v\\'f9ng \\u273?\\u7845?t ch\\u7871?t n\\'e0y. V\\u7915?a v\\u7873? nh\\'e0 m\\u7899?i, ch\\u432?a \\u259?n \\u273?\\u432?\\u7907?c c\\'e1i g\\'ec ngon ng\\u7867? \\u273?\\'e3 b\\u7883? \\u273?i \\u7881?a r\\u7891?i b\\'e0y b\\u7915?a ra. Con ch\\'f3. >_}\\line \\line \\li0\\ri0\\sa0\\sb0\\fi0\\ql\\par}\r\n}\r\n}\r\n}"
